[
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64062_000002_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64062/6324_64062_000002_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "CHAPTER five",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64062_000004_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64062/6324_64062_000004_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "All the foregoing has more or less application to the present topic. We are still dealing with the nocturnal wanderers.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64062_000004_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64062/6324_64062_000004_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "Occasionally any of the above may be discovered abroad in the full glare of day.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64062_000004_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64062/6324_64062_000004_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "Some hunters successfully locate them, by the aid of dogs, in their dens or burrows and capture them in the day-time.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64062_000004_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64062/6324_64062_000004_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "This is a cut and dried operation that requires none of the resourceful tactics of man and dog in the chase, and is, therefore, dismissed from the discussion. Now, what are the dog's duties?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64062_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64062/6324_64062_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "Many hunters pick up many of the skunk on the field, without even being touched by the dogs.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64062_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64062/6324_64062_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "In this connection a contributor writes: \"We walk right up to the skunks and pick them up by the tails; then hit them on the head with a club and kill them or put them in the bag and take them home alive, as the occasion may suit.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64062_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64062/6324_64062_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "The skunk is a foolish, unresourceful animal and were it not for its natural, unique means of defense, would be utterly at the mercy of dogs and hunters.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64062_000008_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64062/6324_64062_000008_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "Many dogs object to the scent and will trail and bring to bay a skunk only with reluctance.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64062_000008_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64062/6324_64062_000008_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "Only those who hunt for profit, care to take the skunk, and he must needs learn the finer points by experience.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64062_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64062/6324_64062_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "The Scotch Terrier and Beagle should be mink dog.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64062_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64062/6324_64062_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "A Pennsylvania hunter contributes the following to the general fund: a good cross for mink as well as rabbit.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64062_000011_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64062/6324_64062_000011_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "This combination gives the requisite agility needed in coping with mink.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64062_000011_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64062/6324_64062_000011_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "Some even advise a strain of water Spaniel with the above breed for ideal.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64062_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64062/6324_64062_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "\"Before taking him out you can teach the young dog when eight or ten months old, what to do by catching an animal that you wish to train your dog on and leading it around.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64062_000012_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64062/6324_64062_000012_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "Loose your dog and let him trail until he finds it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64062_000012_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64062/6324_64062_000012_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "Teach the dog to bark by hissing him on and clapping, whooping to him and such like.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64062_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64062/6324_64062_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "If for skunk, kill one and drag it around, place it out of pup's reach, and teach him to bark when he comes upon his game.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64062_000013_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64062/6324_64062_000013_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "You can teach the habit of tongueing after night or silence on the trail as you prefer.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64062_000013_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64062/6324_64062_000013_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "These two breeds are good ones for any kind of night hunting.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64062_000014_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64062/6324_64062_000014_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "I believe what I have told will generally break any dog.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64062_000015_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64062/6324_64062_000015_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "Always pet him and be friendly after chastising him, and a good scolding with a couple of light smacks with open hand will take the place of a whipping.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64062_000015_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64062/6324_64062_000015_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "Don't use a stick unless necessary.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64062_000015_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64062/6324_64062_000015_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "Use judgment, the same as you would want some one to use you, and in a few nights' training your dog will be catching game.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64062_000015_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64062/6324_64062_000015_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "It is easy sailing after a few are caught, and your dog is your greatest friend you have.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64063_000001_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64063/6324_64063_000001_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "CHAPTER six.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64063_000002_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64063/6324_64063_000002_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "WOLF AND COYOTE HUNTING.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64063_000003_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64063/6324_64063_000003_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "Training a dog to hunt young wolves is a harder task, and unless your dog is born for it, you will fail to make anything like a first class dog out of him.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64063_000003_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64063/6324_64063_000003_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "Almost any good fox dog will hunt old wolves, but very few will hunt pups, and my experience has been that a bitch will hunt quicker than a dog.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64063_000004_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64063/6324_64063_000004_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "There are plenty of dogs that will hunt and trail wolves all right, but very few that will hunt the pups.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64063_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64063/6324_64063_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "Sometimes when your dog trails in near the pups you will get a fight, and sometimes they will jump out and run for it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64063_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64063/6324_64063_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "Sometimes if the pups are quite young you will find the mother in with them and for the first few days she will be found near them, but as they grow older she will be found farther away.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64063_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64063/6324_64063_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "English blue are very fast and the stag are long winded and have the grit to make a good fight.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64063_000012_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64063/6324_64063_000012_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "I only hunt in spring and late in fall, but any time is good when you can find them.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64063_000012_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64063/6324_64063_000012_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "But don't take your dogs out in summer, as it will be sure to be the time when you will find a hard race, and there is where you will hurt some of your best dogs.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64063_000012_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64063/6324_64063_000012_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "I use a pack of from three to five, but the more the better.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64063_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64063/6324_64063_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "I want a dog that will weigh seventy five pounds, with long legs and short back so he can gather himself up quickly.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64063_000014_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64063/6324_64063_000014_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "I don't think foxhounds are any good for wolves.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64063_000014_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64063/6324_64063_000014_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "I have seen thirty five of them start after the same wolf, in good weather and four hours afterward there were only two, the smallest of the pack, still in the race.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64063_000014_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64063/6324_64063_000014_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "I have no doubt but that they could have taken the wolf several times in the race, but all they could do was to bark.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64063_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64063/6324_64063_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "I will not say a full blood stag hound is not all right, in a level, unobstructed country, but in many parts of the country many large dogs would not be able to get thru the fences or over the rough ground with the ease that the smaller ones do.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64063_000016_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64063/6324_64063_000016_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "I have never seen the big dog that could catch and kill a wolf by himself.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64063_000016_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64063/6324_64063_000016_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "I have killed them with two, but would rather have four or five.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64063_000017_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64063/6324_64063_000017_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "I always hunt on a horse, and they should be the best of horses, well broken and not afraid of wire.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64063_000017_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64063/6324_64063_000017_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "I never carry a gun of any kind, but always have a hammer, and if I want to succor the dogs in the race, I will ride up to the dogs and kill the wolf for them.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64063_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64063/6324_64063_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "The Irish wolfhound of history is no more, the breed having become extinct years ago.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64063_000019_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64063/6324_64063_000019_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "Other combinations have also been tried, with more or less good effect.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64063_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64063/6324_64063_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "The minimum height and weight of dogs should be thirty one inches and one hundred twenty pounds; bitches twenty eight inches and ninety pounds.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64063_000021_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64063/6324_64063_000021_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "Anything below this should be debarred from competition.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64063_000021_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64063/6324_64063_000021_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "Great size, including height and shoulder and proportionate length of body is the desideratum to be aimed at, and it is desired to firmly establish a race that shall average from thirty two to thirty four inches in dogs, showing the requisite power, activity, courage and symmetry.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64063_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64063/6324_64063_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "\"The coat should be rough and hard on body, legs and head; especially wiry and long over the eyes and under the jaws.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64063_000022_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64063/6324_64063_000022_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "The recognized colors are gray, brindle, red, black, pure white, fawn or any color that appears in the deerhound.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64063_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64063/6324_64063_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "THE RUSSIAN WOLFHOUND.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6324_64063_000024_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6324/64063/6324_64063_000024_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6324",
        "content": "The Russian wolfhound has a reputation for being a most capable wolf catcher in his native country, but so far the pure bred hound of that family has not held his own with the American wolf.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
